      <title>美联储库克表示私人信贷并未损害金融弹性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/fed-s-cook-says-private-credit-hasn-t-hurt-financial-resilience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，非银行投资公司贷款的增加值得关注，但似乎并未给金融体系带来过度风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/fed-s-cook-says-private-credit-hasn-t-hurt-financial-resilience</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
